      <title>印度在与新西兰进行贸易协议的会谈，因为美国关税织机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/india-in-talks-with-new-zealand-on-trade-deal-as-us-tariffs-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着国家寻求加强经济关系，印度已经开始就与新西兰达成的自由贸易协定进行谈判，这是全球贸易不确定性的增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/india-in-talks-with-new-zealand-on-trade-deal-as-us-tariffs-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 12:03:36 GMT</pubDate>
