    <item>
      <title>几个月来最便宜的大型科技库存无法吸引警惕的买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/big-tech-stocks-at-cheapest-in-months-fail-to-entice-wary-buyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在最近的市场抛售中，大型技术公司的估值已从崇高的高度降低。不过，许多交易者押注，下降很可能还有进一步的发展，而最近的历史提供了证据来支持他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/big-tech-stocks-at-cheapest-in-months-fail-to-entice-wary-buyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
